        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 11 at 4:05PM EDT by NWS Peachtree City GA</headline>
        <description>At 405 PM EDT, a strong thunderstorm was over Tuckers Crossroad, or 9
miles north of Dublin, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Up to penny sized hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to exposed surfaces is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Lovett, Spann, Tuckers Crossroad, Brewton, Scott, and Wrightsville.
</description>
        <instruction>People outdoors should seek shelter immediately.</instruction>
